{"tid":386362,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港姐十號張寶欣入一入黎😭","createTime":"2017-09-03T20:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T18:03:40.000Z","uid":126447,"like":256,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"165d987dee3dbb9226b538ecae538e0270f2b04e","tid":386362,"uid":126447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:26:44.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母靠關係入十強<br />\n入到十強仲搶9埋人地bbc 個獎<br />\n又柒又無氣質 講野1999又鳩笑<br />\n想做港姐？發夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019efe80f9b2dc280fef9b14e331023804f069d0","tid":386362,"uid":92376,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BBC最受歡迎香港小姐數據分析<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=257bb87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據mytv個時間 17:42個陣10號個累積數量係704990<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=deb3a36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19:13個陣10號個累積數量係757943<br />\n<br />\n總時間長度=19:13-17:42=91秒<br />\n數量增長=757943-704990=52953<br />\n增長速率=52953/91=582/秒<br />\n<br />\n根據賽前BBC記錄 10號同9號有明顯差距<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c861a540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10號同9號差距=1768205-698644=1069561<br />\n<br />\n假設10號一直保持同一個速率去追<br />\n假設9號今晚完全冇增長<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10號超越9號所需時間=1069561/582=1838秒=31分鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n成個環節頭尾應該冇30分鐘 仲要未計9號今晚個增長 <br />\n完全睇唔到10號會贏個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母還返個獎比9號啦臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd27fe97f903d50994e5bb0f8490fb8f373fef7c","tid":386362,"uid":83578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:35:48.000Z","msg":"平時唔係會請黃龍德 會計師<br />\nLEE次有冇?"},{"pid":"fa32519ebb3edfa1e17960a5b9dd9b96f7a01f5b","tid":386362,"uid":92376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:36:16.000Z","msg":"豬肉獎都貪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知唔知醜字點寫架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebb5f663ce326dc26bd336c0052a5e781a17791","tid":386362,"uid":92376,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:37:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時唔係會請黃龍德 會計師<br />\nLEE次有冇?</blockquote><br />\n今晚真係好似無講過有黃龍德或者羅兵咸永道果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係咪可以投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774b500e69b56e3850ef1c98be4b34ff5d25e46a","tid":386362,"uid":83578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T20:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時唔係會請黃龍德 會計師<br />\nLEE次有冇?</blockquote><br />\n今晚真係好似無講過有黃龍德或者羅兵咸永道果啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁係咪可以投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n似鬼鬼地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfd42c52f607b5e805fe99d058fb0291a283522","tid":386362,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:18:02.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係寶欣呀。"},{"pid":"b0fdf03e6fc032ff4016c0b56228fcfc80948d2e","tid":386362,"uid":92376,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquo